                HNF1B‐
                associated clinical traits. Overall, both mutation groups showed a high phenotypic heterogeneity. The reclassification of all previously reported intragenic
                HNF1B
                variants provided an up‐to‐date overview of the mutational spectrum.
              
            
            
              Conclusions
              
                We highlight the value of prenatal
                HNF1B
